column6: Family Ranch House located in Historic Walburg.\nCovered porch and Patio with raised Deck. House overlooks the 170 acre Heritage Ranch including an active cattle operation, (3) Stock Tanks with Catch & Release Fishing. (Pre-Authorization & Check TX License Requirements) and adjacent to the Central Texas Olive Ranch Orchard. Master Suite w Bath and two additional Private Bedrooms w Hollywood style shared bath. Additional bath off Study/Laundry room. Walburg is home to two Beir Garten Restaurants.
